data.description: Looking for One Story Living?  Diamond in the Rough alert!  Don't miss This One Story, 1700sqft Rancher. Nestled in East Mt. Airy.   This location is close to parks, shopping, regional rail and other transportation.   This Rancher boast of 4 nice size Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms , Spacious Livingroom (with fireplace), Formal Dining room and large Kitchen space.  Offering hardwood flooring throughout, this home is all on the first floor giving your the ability to maneuver with ease around the house. All this diamond needs is a little TLC to make it Shine. The property was converted from radiator heat to central air several years back.   Four bonuses: 1) This property sits on a 9800sqft lot with a 2(two) car detached garage.  At least 5-6 cars can park in the driveway comfortably.  2). the basement is also about the same size footprint as the 1st floor and nice and open. The basement is partially finished, with a 1/2 bath and  backyard access. 3).  The property has a very spacious walk up attic with a massive amount of storage space.  4). This home has a new roof,.  The old roof was completely removed and replaced with a totally new roof. (50 year warranty on labor and materials on any manufacturer defects. 10 yr warranty on instalation errors.) Don't miss it!
